                <note type="updated" update="title" import="tengyur-data-1425-1540_PH_new_v2.4.xml" date-time="2021-11-02T13:18:33.485Z" user="admin">According to Tsong-kha-pa (Toh. 5390), Abhayākaragupta provides an etymology of the title saying that it is like "springtime" (dpyid) because when the inner
